WEBVTT

01:36.940 --> 01:40.979
[The Best Thing]

01:41.400 --> 01:48.680
[Episode 21: Tulips]
[Bitter and pungent in taste, neutral in nature, enters the lung meridian, transforms dampness, and dispels foulness.]

02:14.190 --> 02:15.840
Are you meeting us at the old house,

02:15.840 --> 02:17.280
or going straight to the cemetery?

02:29.560 --> 02:32.160
Something urgent came up, so I won't be going to Hang City this year.

02:33.000 --> 02:35.390
I've ordered a bouquet of tulips to be delivered to the old house.

02:36.040 --> 02:37.720
Bring it to Nian for me.

02:46.320 --> 02:46.980
Mom.

02:47.910 --> 02:49.030
Suye is here.

02:53.190 --> 02:53.820
Mom.

02:55.510 --> 02:56.790
What are you reading?

02:57.700 --> 03:00.190
When they were stopping my bleeding earlier,

03:02.240 --> 03:04.800
I suddenly thought of a TCM herb for stopping bleeding,

03:06.630 --> 03:08.630
but I can't remember its name no matter how hard I try.

03:10.590 --> 03:13.000
I studied TCM since I was young,

03:14.560 --> 03:16.770
but now I can't even remember the name of a single herb.

03:19.890 --> 03:22.560
It must be a side effect of the brain metastasis, right?

04:10.580 --> 04:11.400
He Suye.

04:12.750 --> 04:14.190
I'm glad I made it in time.

04:14.600 --> 04:15.600
Why are you here?

04:16.100 --> 04:17.420
I picked these flowers for your mom.

04:17.450 --> 04:18.600
I was thinking if you could give them to her for me.

04:18.730 --> 04:19.970
I hope she likes them.

04:44.890 --> 04:46.100
She will like them.

05:14.510 --> 05:15.270
Nian,

05:16.340 --> 05:18.650
He Sheng is too busy with work to come,

05:19.320 --> 05:20.880
so I came with Suye.

05:21.560 --> 05:22.310
But

05:22.520 --> 05:24.000
he asked us to bring you

05:24.030 --> 05:25.600
your favourite tulips.

05:25.920 --> 05:27.260
Don't be disappointed, alright?

05:30.470 --> 05:32.100
As for me, rest assured,

05:32.630 --> 05:33.870
I'm in good health.

05:34.800 --> 05:37.530
This time, your son is bringing you good news.

05:38.420 --> 05:39.190
Let me tell you,

05:39.190 --> 05:40.700
he finally has a girlfriend.

05:42.200 --> 05:44.850
Let your son properly introduce her to you.

05:46.830 --> 05:47.570
Mom,

05:48.670 --> 05:49.870
her name is Shen Xifan.

05:50.430 --> 05:53.280
She's a very intelligent and cheerful girl.

05:54.480 --> 05:57.230
I feel very happy spending time with her every day.

05:58.600 --> 05:59.480
Besides,

06:00.500 --> 06:01.790
she likes flowers too.

06:03.120 --> 06:04.190
She's the one

06:04.670 --> 06:06.110
who chose the flowers for you this year.

06:07.480 --> 06:08.180
However,

06:09.110 --> 06:10.670
she has to go study abroad this year.

06:11.960 --> 06:14.790
I'll bring her to see you two years later.

06:15.970 --> 06:17.320
I hope you'll like her.

06:17.870 --> 06:18.390
She will.

06:19.130 --> 06:21.450
I believe your mom will definitely like her.

06:23.920 --> 06:24.600
Mom,

06:25.270 --> 06:26.510
there's another piece of good news.

06:27.270 --> 06:28.430
My research on breast cancer

06:28.430 --> 06:29.660
is also on track now.

06:30.790 --> 06:33.040
I'll definitely work hard to do it well.

06:33.860 --> 06:35.390
Nian, did you hear that?

06:36.370 --> 06:38.010
The topic your son is researching on

06:38.480 --> 06:41.270
will benefit all breast cancer patients.

06:42.310 --> 06:43.830
It's to allow all patients

06:44.270 --> 06:45.760
to complete their final journey

06:46.060 --> 06:47.890
with dignity.

06:48.270 --> 06:49.510
If you can hear us from heaven,

06:50.510 --> 06:52.270
please bless your son's

06:52.270 --> 06:54.300
research project with success.

07:01.250 --> 07:05.950
[Beloved wife, Yu Nianxiang]

07:04.750 --> 07:05.720
Stop thinking about it.

07:06.550 --> 07:09.380
Your father has a new family to take care of.

07:09.480 --> 07:10.920
It's normal that he couldn't come.

07:12.090 --> 07:14.530
You brought such beautiful fresh flowers this year.

07:14.560 --> 07:15.680
How lovely they are!

07:16.350 --> 07:18.310
And such good news too.

07:19.390 --> 07:22.070
I believe your mom would be very happy.

07:23.690 --> 07:26.080
Miss Shen is really thoughtful.

07:26.520 --> 07:28.030
You should thank her properly.

07:30.030 --> 07:32.100
Is she on leave at home today?

07:32.600 --> 07:33.480
She's on duty.

07:34.110 --> 07:34.920
On duty, I see.

07:36.170 --> 07:38.820
Is it convenient to give her a call then?

07:39.500 --> 07:40.380
Let me ask her.

07:57.830 --> 07:58.659
Are you busy?

08:03.750 --> 08:04.720
Not at all.

08:05.060 --> 08:05.940
What's up?

08:09.160 --> 08:10.230
Can we have a video call?

08:10.480 --> 08:11.990
Grandpa wants to greet you.

08:21.970 --> 08:23.370
Okay, okay.

08:32.470 --> 08:33.240
Is it tiring to work

08:33.240 --> 08:34.030
over the holiday?

08:35.390 --> 08:36.309
It's alright.

08:36.330 --> 08:37.760
There aren't many people during the Qingming holiday.

08:37.919 --> 08:38.590
How about you?

08:39.549 --> 08:40.870
I'm fine.

08:41.100 --> 08:43.409
I just drove over to chat with my mom.

08:49.020 --> 08:49.590
Wait a moment.

08:53.370 --> 08:54.930
Hello, Miss Shen.

08:55.700 --> 08:57.180
I'm not disturbing your work, am I?

08:57.790 --> 08:58.360
No, not at all.

08:58.360 --> 08:59.150
Not even a bit.

08:59.170 --> 09:00.480
It's been a long time, Professor Yu.

09:02.200 --> 09:03.670
Thank you for the flowers.

09:03.670 --> 09:04.670
They're beautiful.

09:04.950 --> 09:07.220
I thank you on behalf of Suye's mother.

09:10.000 --> 09:11.520
You've tied your hair up.

09:11.550 --> 09:12.950
It makes you look very energetic.

09:13.460 --> 09:14.980
Your complexion has improved a lot too.

09:15.120 --> 09:17.310
Suye's treatment for you seems quite effective.

09:17.330 --> 09:19.260
Of course, that goes without saying.

09:19.910 --> 09:21.030
It's been effective.

09:21.610 --> 09:23.480
You look very energetic too.

09:24.200 --> 09:25.440
It's because I'm happy.

09:25.900 --> 09:26.780
Miss Shen,

09:26.810 --> 09:28.090
will you be working overtime tomorrow?

09:28.450 --> 09:29.760
I won't be working overtime tomorrow.

09:30.130 --> 09:30.930
That's great!

09:31.390 --> 09:33.650
Tomorrow, I will go for a walk

09:33.870 --> 09:35.610
in the herbal garden with Suye.

09:35.760 --> 09:37.760
Do you and your family want to come along?

09:37.780 --> 09:39.020
If it's not abrupt, that is.

09:41.190 --> 09:43.480
You know, as an old man living alone,

09:43.510 --> 09:45.220
holidays can be quite boring.

09:45.710 --> 09:48.620
If you and your family don't mind,

09:48.730 --> 09:51.090
consider it a countryside excursion.

09:51.120 --> 09:52.920
Don't feel any pressure.

09:53.590 --> 09:54.350
No, no.

09:54.440 --> 09:55.480
There's no pressure at all.

09:55.510 --> 09:58.080
Is it the herbal garden from the medicated diet project last time?

09:58.100 --> 09:58.730
Yes, yes, that's right.

10:00.100 --> 10:01.390
I really like that place.

10:01.410 --> 10:02.300
No problem.

10:02.340 --> 10:03.690
I'll ask my parents about it later.

10:03.720 --> 10:07.510
Alright, alright, then I'll wait for your response.

10:07.690 --> 10:08.270
Good.

10:10.850 --> 10:11.910
Alright, alright.

10:12.130 --> 10:13.590
Go ask Mr. and Mrs. Shen about it.

10:14.050 --> 10:14.840
Tonight,

10:14.860 --> 10:16.740
I'll be staying over at my grandpa's.

10:18.040 --> 10:19.920
Miss Shen, see you tomorrow.

10:21.370 --> 10:22.150
Bye-bye,

10:22.150 --> 10:23.290
Dr. He.

10:24.860 --> 10:25.610
Bye-bye.

10:28.020 --> 10:29.380
Spring has arrived.

10:30.270 --> 10:31.260
Talking about yourself?

10:33.130 --> 10:34.300
Let's get going.

10:35.470 --> 10:35.990
Let's go.

10:39.930 --> 10:41.570
Can you two help me decide?

10:41.600 --> 10:43.840
Which of these two should I wear tomorrow?

10:44.380 --> 10:45.940
I... I want to wear a dress.

10:45.970 --> 10:47.330
I don't want to wear sportswear.

10:47.620 --> 10:48.860
Wear sportswear is better.

10:48.890 --> 10:51.650
It's not convenient for you to wear a dress while climbing up and down.

10:51.990 --> 10:52.990
Ms. Shen has already said

10:53.010 --> 10:54.090
that place is particularly difficult to access.

10:54.120 --> 10:55.970
Since we're finally going, I have to take some photos, right?

10:56.170 --> 10:58.690
This one will definitely look better in photos.

10:58.720 --> 10:59.840
No, look at this colour.

10:59.840 --> 11:00.880
Do you actually think it's pretty?

11:01.310 --> 11:03.100
It won't look good on you because your skin is dark.

11:03.160 --> 11:04.800
This would only look good on fair-skinned people.

11:04.820 --> 11:05.580
Then, the dress

11:05.760 --> 11:06.610
is okay, I guess.

11:06.650 --> 11:08.290
There aren't be many people during the Qingming holiday.

11:08.310 --> 11:08.950
What about you?

11:09.870 --> 11:11.000
I'm fine.

11:11.410 --> 11:13.820
I just drove over to chat with my mom.

11:15.680 --> 11:16.720
Is it okay, Ms. Shen?

11:18.940 --> 11:19.500
It's fine.

11:19.900 --> 11:20.830
It's settled then.

11:21.630 --> 11:22.390
Dad, Mom,

11:23.320 --> 11:25.920
I have something I want to discuss with you two.

11:26.240 --> 11:26.860
Have a seat.

11:31.190 --> 11:34.360
He Suye's mother passed away many years ago.

11:34.520 --> 11:36.900
He went to sweep his mother's grave,

11:37.240 --> 11:40.950
so he won't be in a great mood tomorrow.

11:41.430 --> 11:44.040
Can we just...

11:44.060 --> 11:45.000
You mean...

11:45.250 --> 11:47.890
I get it. You don't want us to bring it up, right?

11:47.910 --> 11:48.380
Yes.

11:49.760 --> 11:50.830
We won't mention it.

11:50.850 --> 11:53.940
We understand. His grandfather is a TCM practitioner, right?

11:53.970 --> 11:54.390
Yes.

11:55.070 --> 11:57.980
We'll just ask about health preservation and wellness.

11:58.000 --> 11:58.710
Things like this.

11:59.070 --> 11:59.630
Sure.

11:59.630 --> 12:02.240
Don't worry, your mother and I know what we're doing.

12:02.240 --> 12:04.080
Tomorrow, let's just have a

12:04.080 --> 12:05.890
relaxing and enjoyable outing, okay?

12:07.290 --> 12:08.640
Thank you both.

12:09.770 --> 12:10.910
Let's not bring up the matter of the dowry.

12:12.640 --> 12:14.050
And no bride price either.

12:15.850 --> 12:17.440
Come on, let's see what I should wear.

12:35.840 --> 12:37.000
Do you know what flower this is?

12:37.040 --> 12:39.040
What flower is this? A small purple flower.

12:39.060 --> 12:40.310
It's so clean.

12:40.480 --> 12:41.590
Take a sniff.

12:41.720 --> 12:42.520
I won't smell it, you smell it.

12:42.640 --> 12:43.520
You smell it.

12:46.240 --> 12:47.470
It doesn't have any scent.

12:47.920 --> 12:48.760
Let me take a photo of you.

12:48.780 --> 12:49.540
It looks pretty nice like this.

12:49.570 --> 12:49.950
Okay.

12:57.360 --> 12:58.310
It's really clean.

12:58.870 --> 13:00.670
Come help me take a full-body photo.

13:00.670 --> 13:01.970
Here, here, hurry up!

13:01.990 --> 13:02.540
Alright!

13:05.470 --> 13:06.020
Okay.

13:06.050 --> 13:06.930
Let me see.

13:07.750 --> 13:08.360
This tree doesn't look good.

13:08.360 --> 13:09.580
Why are my feet not in it?

13:09.620 --> 13:11.100
Full-body, I said full-body!

13:12.000 --> 13:12.960
Let me take a look.

13:13.480 --> 13:14.150
This way, this way, this way.

13:14.150 --> 13:15.480
What is that?

13:15.480 --> 13:16.190
He Suye.

13:16.390 --> 13:17.120
Include my legs.

13:20.900 --> 13:21.420
No.

13:21.480 --> 13:22.030
It's not working.

13:22.870 --> 13:23.420
Okay.

13:25.360 --> 13:26.430
This one is passable.

13:26.460 --> 13:27.950
Ms. Liu, this was taken nicely, wasn't it?

13:27.970 --> 13:28.880
Yes, that's fine.

13:29.980 --> 13:31.260
What did you call her?

13:31.680 --> 13:32.490
I called her Ms. Liu.

13:34.110 --> 13:35.390
It's our family's official title.

13:36.130 --> 13:37.080
Then what do you call him?

13:37.110 --> 13:38.200
Mr. Shen.

13:39.150 --> 13:39.790
I'm an English teacher

13:39.790 --> 13:41.120
in a high school.

13:41.980 --> 13:42.910
What about Shen?

13:43.390 --> 13:44.000
Ms. Shen.

13:45.090 --> 13:45.700
Look.

13:47.720 --> 13:49.200
Your family is so interesting.

13:49.230 --> 13:50.440
We're just joking around.

13:50.460 --> 13:50.940
Yes, yes, yes.

13:50.960 --> 13:51.830
Look, my grandfather

13:51.870 --> 13:53.120
just learned that your family

13:53.120 --> 13:53.720
addresses each other like this.

13:53.720 --> 13:54.480
He's curious.

13:54.640 --> 13:56.680
Then how will you address me?

13:56.700 --> 13:57.820
Professor Yu.

13:58.190 --> 13:59.270
Let's go with Professor Yu.

13:59.290 --> 13:59.910
Right, right, right.

13:59.910 --> 14:00.910
We'll call you Professor Yu.

14:00.910 --> 14:01.960
Professor Yu.

14:01.960 --> 14:02.510
You see.

14:02.510 --> 14:04.200
This way, we're like one big family.

14:04.200 --> 14:05.320
Yes, yes, yes.

14:06.230 --> 14:07.780
How much we resemble a family!

14:10.030 --> 14:11.390
Come on.

14:13.230 --> 14:15.180
Three, two, one.

14:15.800 --> 14:16.370
Good.

14:16.950 --> 14:18.590
You two come and take a photo too.

14:19.820 --> 14:21.340
I'll pass.

14:21.480 --> 14:23.050
Professor Yu, come take a photo.

14:23.070 --> 14:24.670
It's not often we come to such a beautiful place.

14:25.110 --> 14:26.350
You and He Suye together.

14:26.510 --> 14:27.000
Hurry.

14:27.000 --> 14:27.330
Come on.

14:28.430 --> 14:29.390
Come, come, come.

14:29.410 --> 14:30.210
Okay.

14:30.470 --> 14:31.520
You take the photo.

14:32.590 --> 14:33.230
I'll take it.

14:33.370 --> 14:33.840
Alright.

14:37.030 --> 14:38.860
Three, two, one.

14:41.540 --> 14:42.730
You guys are too serious.

14:42.760 --> 14:44.090
Liven up a bit.

14:44.120 --> 14:45.310
Let's take one more with another pose.

14:45.330 --> 14:46.490
No more photos.

14:46.520 --> 14:47.520
I'm old now.

14:47.540 --> 14:48.810
I don't like taking photos anymore.

14:49.440 --> 14:50.840
One photo is enough.

14:52.120 --> 14:52.670
Shen,

14:52.970 --> 14:54.500
why don't you take a photo with Suye?

14:54.670 --> 14:55.950
I'll take it for you two.

14:57.170 --> 14:58.200
Okay? Come on.

14:58.230 --> 14:58.870
Alright.

14:59.170 --> 15:00.030
You're taking it?

15:00.030 --> 15:00.720
I'll take it.

15:00.740 --> 15:02.930
Tell me how to use this phone.

15:07.420 --> 15:08.080
Yes.

15:08.110 --> 15:08.790
Is it like this?

15:08.790 --> 15:09.240
Yes, yes, yes.

15:09.240 --> 15:11.240
That's right, like that. Now it's clear.

15:11.240 --> 15:12.070
Okay, okay.

15:12.100 --> 15:13.030
Look here.

15:16.180 --> 15:17.220
Relax.

15:17.750 --> 15:18.320
Okay.

15:38.400 --> 15:39.090
Okay.

15:41.240 --> 15:41.880
Alright.

15:41.900 --> 15:42.260
One.

15:42.290 --> 15:42.720
Two.

15:42.740 --> 15:43.110
Three.

15:57.450 --> 15:58.740
This grove is beautiful.

15:59.260 --> 16:00.860
The air is fresh too.

16:03.680 --> 16:05.410
The ones ahead are cinnamon.

16:06.040 --> 16:08.370
Look at this. Do you remember what it is?

16:09.080 --> 16:10.080
It's agarwood!

16:15.690 --> 16:16.930
A familiar scent.

16:17.960 --> 16:19.010
Your memory is quite good.

16:20.610 --> 16:21.250
Let's go.

16:26.570 --> 16:27.690
Last time we came,

16:27.720 --> 16:29.360
there weren't any tulips here, were there?

16:30.240 --> 16:32.240
Well, the tulip blooming season just arrived, didn't it?

16:35.540 --> 16:37.210
Can these tulips be used in medicine?

16:37.230 --> 16:40.590
Yes, they can remove dampness and deodorize.

16:42.720 --> 16:44.050
These aren't for medicinal use.

16:44.080 --> 16:46.920
The medicinal tulips are in the greenhouse up ahead.

16:47.970 --> 16:50.050
But these planted here look quite pretty too.

16:50.210 --> 16:51.140
The yellow ones are beautiful.

16:51.440 --> 16:52.870
I planted these tulips

16:52.870 --> 16:54.540
to commemorate my daughter,

16:54.660 --> 16:57.150
who is also Suye's mother.

16:57.910 --> 16:59.390
Her name is Yu Nianxiang

16:59.730 --> 17:02.880
and her favorite flower was the tulip.

17:03.110 --> 17:04.420
So I asked someone

17:05.260 --> 17:06.980
to plant these tulips.

17:07.859 --> 17:09.450
Every year at this time,

17:10.450 --> 17:12.099
the tulips bloom,

17:12.869 --> 17:13.950
and that's when she knows

17:15.270 --> 17:16.510
we've come to see her.

17:18.710 --> 17:19.270
Let's go.

17:19.400 --> 17:21.550
Let's go see the Paeonia lactiflora garden up ahead.

17:25.020 --> 17:26.260
So,

17:26.470 --> 17:28.950
Auntie's favorite flower was the tulip.

17:29.840 --> 17:30.670
Yes.

17:31.230 --> 17:32.800
She must have loved

17:34.120 --> 17:35.270
the bouquet you prepared yesterday.

17:37.100 --> 17:38.190
Then I can rest easy.

17:58.850 --> 17:59.580
Dr. He,

17:59.690 --> 18:06.000
♫You're like a gentle wind♫

18:00.350 --> 18:01.830
I don't have much to give you.

18:01.990 --> 18:03.030
I'd like to give you these flowers,

18:03.050 --> 18:04.290
double the happiness.

18:06.450 --> 18:12.000
♫After early summer afternoon, it blows past my heart♫

18:07.080 --> 18:07.950
Dr. He.

18:13.310 --> 18:19.510
♫When your fingers touch my hands♫

18:16.760 --> 18:19.600
It's really hard to buy tulips of this colour.

18:19.620 --> 18:20.820
I'll give you half of them.

18:20.240 --> 18:24.860
♫So you're also here for me♫

18:27.260 --> 18:32.850
♫I hear you say, red beans grow in the southern lands♫

18:33.830 --> 18:36.690
♫When spring comes, a few branches begin to sprout♫

18:37.230 --> 18:40.690
♫Cherish the youth♫

18:42.470 --> 18:48.390
♫Loving you is the best thing I've ever done♫

18:49.350 --> 18:54.230
♫Among the vast sea of people, you and I understand each other♫

18:51.010 --> 18:52.090
Do you know

18:53.120 --> 18:54.670
why I like you?

18:56.080 --> 19:02.000
♫Missing you is the most beautiful thing in my life♫

18:56.160 --> 18:57.880
Didn't you say it before,

18:57.910 --> 18:59.280
that I hooked you first?

19:00.300 --> 19:00.970
Yes,

19:02.120 --> 19:03.360
but that's not the whole story.

19:02.940 --> 19:08.150
♫Write it down in your heart and never disappear♫

19:07.240 --> 19:08.350
Before you,

19:09.060 --> 19:11.410
treating patients was just a responsibility to me.

19:13.610 --> 19:15.890
But after you came,

19:16.400 --> 19:19.400
I realized that treating patients could be interesting too.

19:21.900 --> 19:27.730
♫I never wish to wake from my dream♫

19:28.620 --> 19:33.830
♫In the late autumn wind, I hold you close♫

19:34.690 --> 19:35.410
I'll gift this to you.

19:35.440 --> 19:41.490
♫Longing will pass through the vast sea of people♫

19:42.360 --> 19:47.480
♫As long as you come, my waiting won’t be in vain♫

19:43.180 --> 19:44.620
On your first visit,

19:44.640 --> 19:46.960
you folded your registration form into a paper frog.

19:48.890 --> 19:50.170
I remember thinking,

19:49.200 --> 19:54.790
♫I hear you say, red beans grow in the southern lands♫

19:51.030 --> 19:53.670
"Wow, you can actually play with registration forms this way."

19:56.010 --> 19:58.870
♫When spring comes, a few branches begin to sprout♫

19:57.830 --> 19:58.920
And then later,

19:59.230 --> 20:00.790
you even tried to change my prescription,

19:59.400 --> 20:02.870
♫Cherish the youth♫

20:01.290 --> 20:02.570
and doubt my medical ethics,

20:02.910 --> 20:04.060
coming up with all sorts of antics.

20:06.500 --> 20:12.380
♫Loving you is the best thing I've ever done♫

20:07.310 --> 20:08.660
But precisely because of this,

20:09.470 --> 20:12.430
I started looking forward to seeing you every week.

20:13.390 --> 20:19.000
♫Among the vast sea of people, you and I understand each other♫

20:16.820 --> 20:17.690
He Suye.

20:20.140 --> 20:26.060
♫Missing you is the most beautiful poem in my life♫

20:21.040 --> 20:21.950
Me too.

20:26.850 --> 20:32.250
♫Write it down in your heart and never disappear♫

21:01.160 --> 21:06.390
[Hang City Renji TCM Herbs Plantation]

21:08.210 --> 21:08.800
Mrs. Shen.

21:09.310 --> 21:09.510
Here.

21:09.510 --> 21:11.080
You've gone to so much trouble. Thank you.

21:11.710 --> 21:14.340
These are all food served in our staff canteen.

21:14.580 --> 21:15.410
Medicinal food.

21:16.330 --> 21:18.410
Although it might not look as appetising as food sold in restaurants,

21:18.440 --> 21:19.870
the taste is quite good.

21:20.250 --> 21:23.530
They're all medicinal ingredients in season.

21:23.880 --> 21:25.510
I hope you don't mind.

21:25.790 --> 21:26.420
It's wonderful.

21:26.440 --> 21:27.090
Yes.

21:27.140 --> 21:27.790
Mr. Shen.

21:29.390 --> 21:30.310
Let me help you.

21:30.330 --> 21:30.680
No need, no need.

21:30.710 --> 21:31.550
I can manage it myself.

21:31.590 --> 21:33.790
Shen, please sit down, sit.

21:34.120 --> 21:36.600
Let Suye handle these chores.

21:40.070 --> 21:41.550
Good, good.

21:42.510 --> 21:43.210
Professor Yu.

21:43.230 --> 21:44.040
Sit, sit, sit.

21:44.070 --> 21:45.500
I'll go get something.

21:48.650 --> 21:50.480
He, don't be so busy.

21:50.500 --> 21:52.740
It's fine. See if anything else is needed,

21:52.770 --> 21:53.530
I'll go get it for you.

21:53.560 --> 21:55.560
We have everything. Sit down.

21:55.740 --> 21:56.300
Okay.

21:56.730 --> 21:58.180
That's not quite right.

21:58.870 --> 22:00.630
On such a wonderful day like today,

22:00.720 --> 22:02.500
how can we not have wine?

22:05.030 --> 22:06.470
And this bottle of wine

22:07.220 --> 22:08.460
is different from others.

22:08.670 --> 22:11.740
I've infused it with the best ginseng and goji berries.

22:12.550 --> 22:15.270
It's been steeping since the beginning of winter, almost half a year now.

22:15.270 --> 22:19.880
Now is when both the medicinal and alcoholic properties are at their best.

22:22.240 --> 22:23.440
Well...

22:25.780 --> 22:26.820
Since Professor Yu is here,

22:26.850 --> 22:28.200
you should have a drink with him.

22:28.220 --> 22:29.060
Alright, alright, alright.

22:29.110 --> 22:29.790
She allowed.

22:30.010 --> 22:31.420
Good, good, good.

22:31.450 --> 22:31.950
Come on.

22:32.250 --> 22:32.790
Let me help you.

22:32.790 --> 22:33.480
Let me help you.

22:33.480 --> 22:34.240
I'll do it.

22:37.610 --> 22:39.040
It's much better than the wine we have at home.

22:39.550 --> 22:39.880
Well...

22:40.360 --> 22:41.680
It's not in the same league.

22:44.520 --> 22:45.480
Professor Yu, please have some first.

22:45.720 --> 22:46.480
Thank you.

22:47.800 --> 22:48.430
Ms. Liu.

22:49.180 --> 22:50.110
It's fine, give it to me.

22:50.990 --> 22:52.840
Miss Shen, why don't you have some too?

22:53.680 --> 22:54.480
She can handle it.

22:54.920 --> 22:56.240
I'm not very good at drinking.

22:56.270 --> 22:57.440
I can't hold liquor well.

22:57.580 --> 22:59.590
Besides, if my parents drink too much,

22:59.590 --> 23:00.830
I'll have to take them home.

23:00.830 --> 23:01.880
You guys enjoy yourselves.

23:02.400 --> 23:03.040
Alright, alright.

23:03.070 --> 23:04.980
He, have a drink.

23:05.340 --> 23:06.180
Okay, I'll drink.

23:07.800 --> 23:09.360
I thought you couldn't drink much.

23:09.400 --> 23:10.300
-I’m fine.
-Come on.

23:10.750 --> 23:10.960
Cheers.

23:10.960 --> 23:12.110
Let us express our gratitude.

23:12.110 --> 23:13.160
Cheers, Professor Yu.

23:13.160 --> 23:13.960
Thank you.

23:15.240 --> 23:16.480
Help yourself.

23:16.500 --> 23:16.870
Thank you.

23:16.900 --> 23:17.770
Thank you, He.

23:24.550 --> 23:26.270
We're really grateful for

23:26.290 --> 23:27.700
Professor Yu's invitation today,

23:27.730 --> 23:29.900
allowing us to come to such a wonderful place for an outing,

23:30.240 --> 23:31.590
enjoy such good medicated diet,

23:31.590 --> 23:34.550
and most importantly, I could drink such excellent medicinal wine.

23:36.310 --> 23:38.220
I should fulfil my duties as a host, shouldn't I?

23:38.550 --> 23:39.480
Duties as a host?

23:41.020 --> 23:42.390
Don't you know?

23:43.330 --> 23:45.440
I invested in this herbal garden.

23:47.490 --> 23:48.950
Suye also invested a bit.

23:58.750 --> 23:59.470
He Suye,

24:00.290 --> 24:01.550
you didn't

24:01.580 --> 24:04.060
explain this clearly to Miss Shen?

24:05.590 --> 24:06.480
There's nothing to say about this.

24:06.480 --> 24:09.260
You should introduce, how should I put it,

24:09.550 --> 24:12.550
your personal qualifications to Miss Shen.

24:13.610 --> 24:15.240
I must remind you,

24:15.640 --> 24:17.510
you can't shortchange Miss Shen.

24:17.710 --> 24:20.600
Don't always serve her medicinal food at home.

24:21.050 --> 24:22.270
You should go out

24:22.320 --> 24:24.490
and treat her to some nice meals.

24:24.560 --> 24:25.160
Yes.

24:26.040 --> 24:27.520
We really love medicinal cuisine.

24:27.550 --> 24:28.070
Yes, yes, yes.

24:28.090 --> 24:30.010
He even prescribed some medicinal recipes for us.

24:30.860 --> 24:32.340
I didn't know about this.

24:33.710 --> 24:34.320
Come, Mrs. Shen,

24:34.350 --> 24:35.200
let me toast to you.

24:35.330 --> 24:36.330
Let's do it altogether.

24:36.870 --> 24:38.390
-Come on, altogether.
-Together.

24:38.590 --> 24:39.440
Another toast to you, Professor Yu.

24:39.440 --> 24:40.750
Good, thank you.

24:40.750 --> 24:43.100
Please, don't stand on ceremony.

24:52.070 --> 24:53.070
Professor Yu, today...

24:53.730 --> 24:54.860
I'm so happy today.

24:56.560 --> 24:57.230
Well then,

24:57.910 --> 24:59.260
when you have time,

25:01.240 --> 25:02.760
welcome to my home.

25:03.350 --> 25:04.920
Come visit my humble abode.

25:05.050 --> 25:07.280
I'd like to prepare some medicinal food for you, if that's alright?

25:07.360 --> 25:08.120
Good, good, good.

25:08.270 --> 25:10.960
Okay.

25:12.950 --> 25:14.440
Where do you live?

25:15.400 --> 25:17.750
We live in the same neighbourhood as He now.

25:17.780 --> 25:18.170
I see.

25:19.550 --> 25:20.830
You live in the same neighbourhood.

25:21.970 --> 25:23.720
What a coincidence!

25:24.230 --> 25:25.470
That's good.

25:26.510 --> 25:28.650
If it's not inconvenient for you,

25:28.670 --> 25:32.340
I'll find time to pay you a visit.

25:32.640 --> 25:33.920
How can this be called a visit?

25:33.960 --> 25:35.850
We're just having a casual meal together.

25:35.880 --> 25:37.750
-Okay?
-Okay.

25:37.770 --> 25:39.620
Just treat it as if you're returning to your own home.

25:39.650 --> 25:40.850
Welcome.

25:40.950 --> 25:41.630
Alright.

25:41.920 --> 25:42.480
Thank you, Mrs. Shen.

25:42.480 --> 25:42.940
Certainly.

25:42.960 --> 25:43.890
Thank you, Professor Yu.

25:44.220 --> 25:45.220
Thank you, Mr. Shen.

25:46.460 --> 25:47.640
Your alcohol tolerance is so high.

25:48.480 --> 25:49.680
I'm happy drinking with you all.

25:50.160 --> 25:51.190
Mr. Shen, have some more.

25:51.420 --> 25:53.050
Alright, then Professor Yu, you...

25:53.080 --> 25:54.080
Ms. Liu.

25:54.490 --> 25:56.450
Professor Yu, I really can't keep up.

25:56.480 --> 25:58.410
Ms. Liu, can you handle it?

25:58.720 --> 26:00.720
I'll fill up Mr. Shen's glass.

26:00.750 --> 26:01.620
No, no, no.

26:01.640 --> 26:02.510
Here.

26:02.510 --> 26:03.830
Grandpa, don't drink too much.

26:03.980 --> 26:05.630
I'm fine.

26:05.680 --> 26:06.030
Look at you...

26:06.030 --> 26:06.990
Look at me.

26:08.040 --> 26:08.600
Mrs. Shen,

26:08.630 --> 26:09.510
if Mr. Shen likes it,

26:09.510 --> 26:10.310
I'll give you some to take home.

26:10.310 --> 26:11.960
Please don't let him drink anymore.

26:11.960 --> 26:12.790
It's fine.

26:12.790 --> 26:13.960
He can really hold his liquor.

26:20.920 --> 26:22.010
You've had too much.

26:24.140 --> 26:24.950
You jerk.

26:27.490 --> 26:28.380
It's fine.

26:28.680 --> 26:29.590
I've only had about 250 ml today.

26:29.590 --> 26:31.110
Take some with you if you like drinking it.

26:32.310 --> 26:33.270
Mr. Shen, have some more.

26:33.540 --> 26:35.150
Alright, then Professor Yu, you...

26:35.650 --> 26:38.110
I'll fill up Mr. Shen's cup first.

26:38.130 --> 26:39.280
Professor Yu, okay.

26:39.310 --> 26:40.600
Okay.

26:40.620 --> 26:41.460
Good, good.

26:41.990 --> 26:43.990
These two kids are destined to meet.

26:45.410 --> 26:46.860
They really are.

26:47.830 --> 26:48.980
I remember

26:49.370 --> 26:53.210
one time, a student of mine had an urgent case

26:53.480 --> 26:55.600
and needed to go to the hospital to help out.

26:56.400 --> 26:58.470
So I went on the house call instead.

26:59.380 --> 27:00.250
The first time...

27:01.010 --> 27:03.410
That is the first time I met Miss Shen.

27:04.690 --> 27:06.380
She was there for a follow-up visit

27:06.790 --> 27:08.830
and left a deep impression on me.

27:09.440 --> 27:11.710
A very beautiful girl

27:12.350 --> 27:13.830
with great aura.

27:14.110 --> 27:14.970
It's hereditary.

27:15.240 --> 27:16.030
Yes, yes, yes.

27:16.030 --> 27:18.130
All the good genes in our family are here.

27:18.160 --> 27:19.400
Yes, yes, yes.

27:19.960 --> 27:21.410
When I came back, I told him.

27:21.880 --> 27:23.470
There was a girl there for a follow-up.

27:23.550 --> 27:24.920
Beautiful and elegant.

27:25.400 --> 27:26.570
I asked "Are you aware?

27:26.590 --> 27:27.620
Do you know her?"

27:27.720 --> 27:30.950
At that time, he looked very depressed,

27:31.610 --> 27:32.620
like it was a pity.

27:32.660 --> 27:33.380
Grandpa.

27:33.510 --> 27:34.640
Enough. Stop talking.

27:34.640 --> 27:36.090
Let me finish what I'm saying.

27:36.120 --> 27:38.230
You were so afraid.

27:38.930 --> 27:40.240
So scared.

27:41.080 --> 27:44.320
Scared of missing this follow-up visit

27:44.400 --> 27:46.790
and that Miss Shen wouldn't come for treatment anymore.

27:46.790 --> 27:48.670
Then, he wouldn't be able to see her again.

27:52.310 --> 27:55.830
After some time, he was very happy one day.

27:55.850 --> 27:59.370
Excited! He said, "Grandpa, Grandpa, do you know?"

27:59.550 --> 28:02.180
"Do you know whose phone number this is?"

28:02.700 --> 28:05.590
I said, "How would I know whose phone number it is?"

28:06.470 --> 28:08.140
"It's the number of

28:08.400 --> 28:11.390
the Miss Shen you mentioned."

28:13.520 --> 28:15.130
He was so excited.

28:15.160 --> 28:15.850
I'm telling you...

28:15.930 --> 28:16.960
Alright, alright, Grandpa.

28:16.990 --> 28:18.600
You've drunk too much. Stop talking.

28:18.620 --> 28:19.540
I'll stop talking.

28:20.190 --> 28:21.230
He's embarrassed.

28:21.310 --> 28:22.360
He's embarrassed.

28:24.200 --> 28:25.120
Come, let's drink.

28:25.270 --> 28:26.510
I... I'll drink with you.

28:26.910 --> 28:27.510
Come on.

28:27.510 --> 28:28.680
Professor Yu, Professor Yu. Come on.

28:28.700 --> 28:29.740
Everyone, please drink less.

28:30.570 --> 28:31.450
Take it easy.

28:31.480 --> 28:32.680
I'm definitely taking it easy.

28:33.010 --> 28:34.340
All of you, please drink less.

28:35.130 --> 28:36.090
He Suye.

28:36.590 --> 28:39.610
Drink more, your alcohol tolerance is good anyway.

28:40.210 --> 28:41.720
If you can drink,

28:42.010 --> 28:43.380
drink more.

28:44.630 --> 28:46.700
I'll deal with you when I get home.

28:55.850 --> 28:57.330
I'm so dizzy.

28:58.020 --> 29:00.000
I'm drunk, I'm drunk.

29:00.030 --> 29:00.810
You're drunk, huh?

29:01.470 --> 29:03.530
Let me check your pulse.

29:10.670 --> 29:12.510
Your body is quite healthy.

29:12.900 --> 29:14.010
Just a bit...

29:14.040 --> 29:14.760
Heartless.

29:18.250 --> 29:19.200
Good that you know.

29:19.410 --> 29:20.410
Switch hands.

29:26.270 --> 29:28.160
Indeed heartless.

29:29.450 --> 29:30.450
You're checking the wrong place.

29:34.100 --> 29:34.820
Give me back the ring.

29:34.940 --> 29:35.640
No.

29:35.920 --> 29:36.960
I can't give you this.

29:37.770 --> 29:39.570
Professor Yu said today that

29:39.790 --> 29:41.150
he went on the house call on your behalf.

29:41.170 --> 29:42.760
That was only my second visit,

29:43.340 --> 29:46.100
which means after my first visit,

29:46.130 --> 29:48.230
you couldn't stop thinking about me.

29:48.580 --> 29:49.690
And now,

29:49.720 --> 29:50.820
you say I hooked you first.

29:51.350 --> 29:52.670
He Suye, give me the ring.

29:52.960 --> 29:54.510
I’m sorry.

29:54.510 --> 29:55.680
Isn't it enough that I admitted I was wrong?

29:57.990 --> 29:58.950
What were you wrong about?

30:02.670 --> 30:04.120
It was clearly me who pursued you first.

30:05.040 --> 30:07.680
But I still slandered you, saying you hooked me.

30:10.270 --> 30:10.880
And then?

30:15.590 --> 30:17.180
Although I did it to pursue you,

30:17.550 --> 30:20.220
I was indeed a bit shameless.

30:21.640 --> 30:22.960
A bit, huh?

30:23.680 --> 30:24.650
And then?

30:25.990 --> 30:26.640
There's more?

30:31.510 --> 30:32.450
I'm a scumbag.

30:35.640 --> 30:36.710
Good that you know.

30:43.560 --> 30:44.470
Don't be angry anymore.

30:44.500 --> 30:45.500
Let go.

30:45.520 --> 30:46.320
I won't.

30:46.790 --> 30:47.640
I'll bite you.

30:48.620 --> 30:49.580
Go ahead and bite.

30:54.970 --> 30:55.740
What are you doing?

31:02.710 --> 31:04.200
What do those ellipsis mean?

31:10.140 --> 31:11.050
Your intention?

31:13.620 --> 31:14.380
I miss you.

32:01.130 --> 32:02.280
Afraid you'll slip away.

32:02.490 --> 32:03.690
Want to hook you again.

32:11.370 --> 32:13.700
Textual evidence. I've taken a screenshot.

32:13.730 --> 32:15.590
Alright, you can make a video call now.

32:30.090 --> 32:31.270
He, come here quickly.

32:31.270 --> 32:32.070
There's a consultation.

32:36.860 --> 32:37.540
Coming, coming.

32:42.440 --> 32:44.520
I believe everyone has already heard.

32:45.060 --> 32:47.630
Thanks to the efforts of our Marketing Department,

32:49.160 --> 32:50.240
in mid-May,

32:50.510 --> 32:53.390
the 8th Summer Conference of the Chinese Medical Association Conference

32:53.420 --> 32:54.830
will be held at our hotel.

32:55.020 --> 32:56.740
It's quite a big event.

32:57.130 --> 32:58.850
Attendees will include top experts from the medical field,

32:58.880 --> 32:59.990
both domestic and international.

33:00.270 --> 33:01.320
All of you here

33:01.340 --> 33:02.720
already have rich experience

33:02.720 --> 33:03.530
in organizing large-scale events.

33:03.720 --> 33:06.000
So I believe we can handle this with ease.

33:23.560 --> 33:24.430
Well...

33:27.950 --> 33:28.680
There's nothing.

33:31.000 --> 33:33.480
It's really thanks to Mr. Lin's efforts

33:33.510 --> 33:35.890
that we get to organise another big event.

33:36.550 --> 33:38.130
Just trying to earn some extra bonus, right?

33:38.160 --> 33:39.450
Later on, let's all take some annual leave together

33:39.480 --> 33:40.930
and go on a trip.

33:41.400 --> 33:43.310
You two can even get double bonus.

33:44.290 --> 33:45.160
What double bonus?

33:45.550 --> 33:46.200
His is his,

33:46.200 --> 33:47.060
and mine is mine.

33:47.480 --> 33:49.550
I hate these big events, they're exhausting.

33:49.650 --> 33:51.140
Enough, enough, enough.

33:51.310 --> 33:53.790
Calm down. Calm down.

33:54.250 --> 33:54.770
Come on,

33:55.270 --> 33:56.160
is my comrade

33:56.160 --> 33:57.760
coming to the medical summit this time?

33:59.640 --> 34:00.480
I don't know.

34:01.550 --> 34:01.960
What's wrong?

34:01.960 --> 34:02.610
Is there something going on?

34:02.640 --> 34:03.360
Tell us.

34:04.750 --> 34:05.670
It's nothing.

34:05.820 --> 34:06.720
It's just that the two of us

34:06.720 --> 34:08.420
were reviewing things at home the other day,

34:08.480 --> 34:10.770
and I realized he was the one who pursued me first.

34:10.800 --> 34:12.210
But before that, he tricked me

34:12.239 --> 34:13.590
and made me take responsibility for him.

34:14.300 --> 34:15.650
My comrade's level of ideological consciousness

34:15.679 --> 34:17.540
really needs improvement.

34:17.570 --> 34:18.870
What should you do in this situation?

34:18.900 --> 34:20.170
You should just aim his face

34:20.199 --> 34:21.199
and slap, slap, slap!

34:21.219 --> 34:22.090
Just hit him!

34:22.120 --> 34:23.480
I'll slap you in the face.

34:23.510 --> 34:24.719
Slap, slap, slap!

34:25.090 --> 34:26.409
That's it.

34:27.730 --> 34:29.250
Just kidding, just kidding.

34:29.280 --> 34:30.010
I'm joking.

34:30.550 --> 34:31.630
But seriously though,

34:31.659 --> 34:33.219
you should really let my comrade come.

34:33.710 --> 34:35.710
It's right in his professional field.

34:35.800 --> 34:36.840
At the same time, he gets to see

34:36.840 --> 34:38.690
your grace while hosting large events.

34:38.889 --> 34:42.080
Who has any grace while hosting big events?

34:42.650 --> 34:44.550
How about we have a few drinks together this weekend?

34:44.650 --> 34:46.120
Invite your Dr. He too.

34:47.050 --> 34:48.530
I can handle my drinks pretty well.

34:48.560 --> 34:50.260
But if he drinks, then...

34:52.030 --> 34:53.630
His behavior when drinking is also concerning, huh?

34:53.850 --> 34:55.210
What do you mean "also"?

34:55.239 --> 34:56.920
My drinking behavior is quite good.

34:58.030 --> 34:58.880
Alright, alright.

34:58.910 --> 34:59.840
We'll invite him then.

34:59.840 --> 35:00.920
Let him come as the designated driver.

35:00.920 --> 35:01.960
-Okay.
-Okay.

35:09.340 --> 35:10.430
How's business?

35:10.560 --> 35:12.080
It's alright. Um...

35:12.100 --> 35:13.570
Dr. He, are you waiting here for your girlfriend to get off work?

35:13.600 --> 35:14.330
Yes, I am.

35:15.070 --> 35:15.800
This is nice.

35:17.270 --> 35:18.140
The bus is coming.

35:18.160 --> 35:19.250
Is it this one?

35:19.310 --> 35:20.060
Oh, yes it is.

35:20.930 --> 35:21.520
Let's chat later.

35:21.550 --> 35:22.280
Okay.

35:32.820 --> 35:34.400
We haven't seen each other all day.

35:34.510 --> 35:35.880
Can't I even have a hug?

35:36.000 --> 35:38.000
I don't want to. I'm afraid you'll trick me again.

35:38.740 --> 35:40.930
Is the trust between us so fragile now?

35:42.040 --> 35:43.290
Then explain to me.

35:43.630 --> 35:45.180
Why did you hang up on my video call today?

35:47.040 --> 35:49.480
I can actually explain this.

35:59.780 --> 36:01.820
Hurry up, hurry up, the consultation is starting.

36:03.260 --> 36:04.230
Oh, I've lost my pen.

36:04.230 --> 36:04.760
Lend me one.

36:04.760 --> 36:05.170
No.

36:05.860 --> 36:07.490
Why are you being so stingy?

36:09.330 --> 36:10.000
Oh, right.

36:11.000 --> 36:13.290
Wait, after the consultation, can you help me with something?

36:13.800 --> 36:14.720
Help with what?

36:16.050 --> 36:17.220
Just help me, that's all.

36:19.190 --> 36:20.960
You won't even lend me a pen.

36:23.440 --> 36:25.960
Today at 8:45 in the morning,

36:25.980 --> 36:28.620
I suddenly needed He for a consultation.

36:29.440 --> 36:32.040
The consultation lasted for about twenty minutes.

36:32.400 --> 36:33.560
Is this alright?

36:33.840 --> 36:35.030
You're still watching?

36:37.470 --> 36:39.200
Didn't I already tell you?

36:39.740 --> 36:41.660
I really didn't hang up on you on purpose.

36:41.690 --> 36:43.360
I really had something urgent come up.

36:45.090 --> 36:46.660
Not necessarily.

36:46.740 --> 36:48.130
He's your colleague.

36:48.160 --> 36:49.520
What if he's covering for you?

36:50.610 --> 36:52.380
Then I'll have to show you the surveillance footage

36:52.410 --> 36:53.730
to prove my innocence.

36:55.000 --> 36:56.160
No, no, no.

36:56.320 --> 36:58.160
I can't trouble others anymore.

36:58.180 --> 36:59.410
I'd feel embarrassed.

37:00.810 --> 37:02.440
I'm not even embarrassed.

37:06.020 --> 37:07.060
Miss Shen,

37:07.380 --> 37:08.610
has your trust in me been restored,

37:08.640 --> 37:10.290
even just a little bit?

37:10.990 --> 37:12.590
Well,

37:13.280 --> 37:15.510
just a tiny bit.

37:24.940 --> 37:25.910
I'm hungry.

37:26.760 --> 37:28.250
Be patient, it'll be ready soon.

37:34.300 --> 37:35.340
Thank you.

37:45.430 --> 37:46.590
Oh, by the way, He Suye,

37:47.030 --> 37:48.590
our hotel is going to host an event for

37:48.590 --> 37:50.320
the Chinese Medical Association.

37:50.340 --> 37:51.260
Did you know about this?

37:52.430 --> 37:54.140
I know about this event. What about it?

37:55.310 --> 37:56.530
Will you be coming?

37:58.520 --> 38:00.120
Grandpa might go,

38:00.150 --> 38:01.170
but I'm not sure about myself.

38:01.670 --> 38:02.750
I'm not qualified enough yet.

38:04.300 --> 38:05.000
Alright.

38:10.050 --> 38:11.340
On Friday,

38:11.370 --> 38:11.730
Xiangya,

38:11.750 --> 38:13.370
Senior Lin, and I

38:13.400 --> 38:15.540
are planning to have a small gathering and drink a bit.

38:15.730 --> 38:16.560
Do you want to join us?

38:17.900 --> 38:19.700
Sure, it's a good chance to relax too.

38:21.540 --> 38:25.020
I'll be drinking then,

38:25.040 --> 38:27.070
so you should be mindful.

38:27.810 --> 38:28.570
I know.

38:29.510 --> 38:31.030
I'll just drink cola, is that okay?

38:35.680 --> 38:36.880
How's the soup today?

38:37.080 --> 38:37.850
It's delicious.

38:37.880 --> 38:38.880
The seasoning is just right.

38:52.580 --> 38:53.320
He.

38:54.580 --> 38:55.100
Director.

38:55.120 --> 38:56.450
Let me tell you something.

38:56.590 --> 38:57.550
Next month,

38:57.570 --> 38:58.740
the Chinese Medical Association

38:58.770 --> 39:01.450
will hold a summer summit in our city.

39:01.840 --> 39:02.510
There'll be a session

39:02.510 --> 39:04.670
for young doctors to present their reports.

39:04.890 --> 39:06.110
The hospital recommended

39:06.110 --> 39:08.000
your research on breast cancer.

39:08.880 --> 39:09.720
Really?

39:10.910 --> 39:12.230
The association's view is that

39:12.330 --> 39:14.930
improving the quality of life of late-stage cancer patients

39:14.960 --> 39:16.840
is a new hot topic in today's society.

39:16.920 --> 39:18.040
They're very interested

39:18.060 --> 39:19.710
and are willing to give you this opportunity.

39:21.520 --> 39:23.080
Of course, the outcome

39:23.110 --> 39:25.360
still depends on your research content.

39:25.380 --> 39:25.980
Yes.

39:26.210 --> 39:27.250
So this week,

39:27.280 --> 39:28.280
make the most of your time

39:28.680 --> 39:31.420
and try to have the report organized and submitted by Monday.

39:31.900 --> 39:33.500
The hospital will submit it to the association

39:33.530 --> 39:35.090
to help you secure this opportunity.

39:35.320 --> 39:36.820
Alright, thank you, Director.

39:39.660 --> 39:41.680
For you new doctors,

39:41.990 --> 39:43.880
this is a great opportunity to stand out.

39:44.130 --> 39:45.900
Others are also eyeing this chance eagerly.

39:46.710 --> 39:47.630
So,

39:47.920 --> 39:49.330
work hard these couple of days

39:49.600 --> 39:51.160
and organize the report well.

39:51.430 --> 39:52.800
Seize this opportunity.

39:54.170 --> 39:54.770
Certainly.

39:56.330 --> 39:56.950
Keep up the good work.

39:57.320 --> 39:58.240
Thank you, Director.

39:58.680 --> 39:59.440
You can go now.

40:17.380 --> 40:18.340
Not off work yet?

40:19.150 --> 40:20.780
I just have a report to write last minute.

40:20.810 --> 40:21.920
You all can head back first.

40:21.940 --> 40:23.790
Then we'll go eat something nice.

40:23.880 --> 40:24.590
Goodbye, Senior He.

40:24.590 --> 40:25.280
Goodbye, Senior He.

40:25.280 --> 40:25.890
What should we eat?

40:25.920 --> 40:26.880
I want to eat grilled fish.

40:27.160 --> 40:28.330
Let's have hot pot.

40:28.670 --> 40:29.790
Grilled fish again?

40:30.320 --> 40:31.440
The hotpot is not that good though.

40:33.550 --> 40:34.280
Then let's head over first.

40:34.280 --> 40:35.480
Alright, we'll go eat first.

40:35.520 --> 40:36.250
You're treating, right?

40:36.280 --> 40:36.880
Okay, I'll treat you.

40:36.880 --> 40:37.870
Bye-bye.

40:54.570 --> 40:55.420
Senior.

40:55.570 --> 40:56.280
Kexin.

40:59.360 --> 41:00.360
It's raining so heavily today.

41:00.360 --> 41:01.670
Yeah, the weather isn't very good.

41:01.670 --> 41:03.630
Right, let's have a meal later.

41:03.630 --> 41:04.800
Sure, what do you want to eat?

41:04.800 --> 41:05.630
Clay pot chicken.

41:05.630 --> 41:06.480
Let's go.

41:07.000 --> 41:07.670
Let's go.

41:25.860 --> 41:27.590
I probably won't be able to make it tonight.

41:28.060 --> 41:28.910
I have to work overtime unexpectedly.

41:33.400 --> 41:34.990
Okay.

41:36.960 --> 41:38.120
I'll come pick you up later.

41:40.040 --> 41:42.330
No need. You focus on your work.

41:48.690 --> 41:50.160
What’s wrong? You're making a face.

41:50.290 --> 41:51.690
He Suye can't make it anymore.

41:51.720 --> 41:52.550
He has to work overtime.

41:52.850 --> 41:54.330
My comrade can't make it?

41:54.840 --> 41:56.070
It's better that he doesn't come.

41:56.100 --> 41:57.500
Let's go have fun together. Come on.
